TITLE: Adding Dynamic Eloquent Relationships to Lunar Models
DESCRIPTION: This example shows how to use Laravel's dynamic relationship resolution to add relationships to Lunar models without extending or replacing them. It demonstrates adding a 'ticket' relationship to the Order model.
SOURCE: https://github.com/lunarphp/lunar/blob/1.x/docs/core/extending/models.md#2025-04-21_snippet_8

LANGUAGE: php
CODE:
```
use Lunar\Models\Order;
