TITLE: Adding Configuration Fields to Custom Field Type
DESCRIPTION: Adding configuration options to a field type using Filament form components. This allows users to customize field behavior through settings in the admin panel.
SOURCE: https://github.com/lunarphp/lunar/blob/1.x/docs/admin/extending/attributes.md#2025-04-21_snippet_2

LANGUAGE: php
CODE:
```
class CustomFieldType extends BaseFieldType
{
    // ...

    public static function getConfigurationFields(): array
    {
        return [
            Grid::make(2)->schema([
                \Filament\Forms\Components\TextInput::make('min_length'),
                \Filament\Forms\Components\TextInput::make('max_length'),
            ]),
        ];
    }
}
```

